<P> <P><b><i>
<font face="Georgia" size="4" color="#9F3215">
Milo Says:
</font></i></b><BR>

   (1) What have you got against cynical bastards?  By the way, get a
dictionary and look for the word "cynic."  It doesn't mean what you
think it means.<P>

   (2) On the contrary, a web page like this is the perfect place for
someone who doesn't like people!<P>

   (3) I've been to France, and I've spoken French to the natives (I've
had a few years of formal training).  They complimented me on my
(admittedly very rough) skills.  Mordez-moi, chienne.<P>

   (4) What does the length of a letter have to do with its value?  What,
all short letters are worthless?  Ten pages of crap is a gold mine?
Help me out.<P>

   (5) You know whose name I see at the top of this web page?
MINE.  If I don't think that a question deserves a serious answer, then
the person who asked it is just going to have to eat it and smile.<P>

   (6) I've tried to answer your last question, but I'm falling asleep at
the keybo....<P>
